  "title": "chore: add .prettierrc",
  "body": "We rely on ESLint for our Prettier configuration but when using Jest's `expect().toMatchInlineSnapshot()`, the Prettier configuration is not used (the file gets overwritten with the default Prettier config).\r\n\r\nWith `.prettierrc`, we ensure that we all work with the same Prettier configuration, including this Jest functionality.",
